data.description: Spacious, Light-Filled End Unit Townhome in Desired Sienna! Inviting Entrance Leading to Main Level with Open Floor Plan.  Large Living Room with Lots Of Windows, Vaulted Ceiling and Fireplace.  Dining Room with Access to Large Balcony for Relaxing and BBQing. Gorgeous Kitchen with 40" Maple Cabinets, Granite Countertop, Stainless Steel Appliances and Breakfast Area! Open Loft *Library*3 rd Bedroom Option! Primary Bedroom Suite with Two Large Closets and Full En-Suite Bathroom. Second Bedroom with Large Closet spaces. English Lower Level Family Room with Bright Windows which Is Great for Entertainment*Play Room*Bedroom, 3 Full Bathrooms.   Laundry Room with Full Size Washer and Dryer! Great Floor Plan! Oversized 2.5 Car Garage. Maintenance Free Community with Fantastic Bike Trail and Just Steps To a Nature Preserve and The Newly Rebuilt Avalon Sienna Playground. Pet Friendly Complex . Excellent Location Close To Shopping, Restaurants, Schools, Transportation and Metro.
